ata-recommend-id=\"image://28c449549a30c4585ea5561ce164ffce\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A featured image with user reviews for Red Dead Redemption.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen \u003cem\u003eRed Dead Redemption\u003c/em\u003e launched initially on PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360, I was still in my senior year of high school. I didn’t have much time to complete such a monumental open-world adventure. So, despite spending countless hours exploring the Wild West, \u003cem\u003eRDR \u003c/em\u003efell on the back burner until the following summer, when I finally sat down one weekend to grind through the entire story. What an experience! - Brandon Morgan \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/red-dead-redemption-remaster-steam-reviews-price-1851690842\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/red-dead-redemption-remaster-steam-reviews-price-1851690842\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477\" data-recommend-id=\"image://938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Rook wears a Mass Effect-themed armor set in his room.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Rook wears a Mass Effect-themed armor set in his room.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Rook wears a Mass Effect-themed armor set in his room.\" data-chomp-id=\"938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Rook wears a Mass Effect-themed armor set in his room.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: BioWare / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477\" data-recommend-id=\"image://938f1eb618af0a22cb85ada4a4837477\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Rook wears a Mass Effect-themed armor set in his room.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s N7 Day, the annual \u003cem\u003eMass Effect \u003c/em\u003eholiday in which BioWare gestures at the next game while fans have a field day with merch and fan art. But this year, the team just put out another game, \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;External link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://howl.link/cmmfmezbu3ckb\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://howl.link/cmmfmezbu3ckb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eDragon Age: The Veilguard\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e and doesn’t want to steal the game’s thunder with a bunch of teases for a game that’s still a ways out. However, brand synergy is strong, and BioWare has put some \u003cem\u003eMass Effect\u003c/em\u003e-themed armor sets in \u003cem\u003eThe Veilguard\u003c/em\u003e for free. - Kenneth Shepard \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/dragon-age-veilguard-mass-effect-n7-day-armor-location-1851692131\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/dragon-age-veilguard-mass-effect-n7-day-armor-location-1851692131\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"ac1caa154ee6253d34f0d99094f395a1\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ac1caa154ee6253d34f0d99094f395a1\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1280\" data-height=\"720\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of PowerWash Simulator showing the player\u0026#39;s first-person perspective as they clean a skate park.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of PowerWash Simulator showing the player\u0026#39;s first-person perspective as they clean a skate park.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/ac1caa154ee6253d34f0d99094f395a1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/ac1caa154ee6253d34f0d99094f395a1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"